    returnExplanation: "Returns the maximum sum found over any k consecutive elements.",
    returnFlow: "Initial window [2,1,5] sum=8. Slide: remove 2, add 1 = 7. Remove 1, add 3 = 9. Remove 5, add 2 = 6. Max=9.",
