    codeExample: `def my_permutations(items):
    if len(items) <= 1:
        return [list(items)]
    result = []
    for i, item in enumerate(items):
        rest = items[:i] + items[i+1:]
        for perm in my_permutations(rest):
            result.append([item] + perm)
    return result

letters = ["A", "B", "C"]
perms = my_permutations(letters)
for p in perms:
    print(p)
print(f"Total: {len(perms)}")`,
