    concepts: ["yield", "generator", "lazy evaluation", "next()", "StopIteration"],
    codeExample: `def count_up(start, stop):
    current = start
    while current <= stop:
        yield current
        current += 1

gen = count_up(1, 5)
print(type(gen))
print(next(gen))
print(next(gen))
print(list(gen))`,
