          hint: "Face: border-radius: 50% on an oval. Smile: an outer circle and an inner white half-circle using overflow:hidden to clip the top half. Eyes: parent div is the eye white, ::before is the iris, ::after is the pupil. Experiment with border-radius to get organic shapes."
