          hint: "Auto-save: each input fires oninput/onchange which calls saveSettings(). Load on page load from localStorage. Export: JSON.stringify then Blob + URL.createObjectURL + a.click(). Import: FileReader.readAsText then JSON.parse then applySettings()."
